originalText.text: Janice is an amazing psychoanalyst. I am a therapist myself and found it incredibly hard to find someone who could hold their own with a peer, who felt completely patient and safe, whose opinion and insight I truly respected, and whom I really felt I could trust completely. She has absolutely been a rock for me. I have even made pretty large life choices to make sure that I could continue seeing her. Totally worth it. Trust in the Janice.
